posts.post_title: FS Partial Back Run - All Graded inc Carolina Brights
posts.post_content:
Hello.

I'm selling a partial T206 Jerry Freeman back run.  I am asking $675 delivered.  Heck of a good deal, I think... it's hard to find a Carolina Brights card alone for that price!  

Here is the SGC + PSA pop info. on these included backs:

EPDG (SGC 20 + PSA 15) = Total Pop 35
Polar Bear (SGC 26 + PSA 12) = Total Pop 38
Old Mill (SGC 8 + PSA 15) = Total Pop 23
Carolina Brights (SGC 1 + PSA 5) = Total Pop 6
Piedmont (SGC 91 + PSA 97) = Total Pop 188
Sweet Caporal (SGC 49 + PSA 62) = Total Pop 107
(Population Info. as of April 10, 2015)

Pics below... please PM me if interested,

Richard
